claim.claim-text:
1. A consumable-supplies purchase order method for a system including a customer equipment and a purchase-order processing apparatus that are connected via a communication network, comprising the steps of: 
detecting at a consumable-supplies condition detection unit of the customer equipment whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
transmitting a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity; 
receiving an order-reception message sent by the purchaseorder processing apparatus when the purchase order is received at the purchase-order processing apparatus; and 
displaying an indication of completion of the purchase order on an operation panel of the customer equipment after the orderreception message is received.

2. A consumable-supplies purchase order method for a system including a customer equipment and a purchase-order processing apparatus that are connected via a communication network, comprising the steps of: 
providing an operation panel having a display and a purchaseorder button in the customer equipment; 
detecting at a consumable-supplies condition detection unit of the customer equipment whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
displaying a purchase-order message related to the consumable-supplies, on the display when the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity; 
setting the purchase-order button in an active state; and 
transmitting a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when the purchase-order button is pressed.

3. A consumable-supplies purchase order method for a system including a customer equipment and a purchase-order processing apparatus that are connected via a communication network, comprising the steps of: 
providing an operation panel having a display in the customer equipment; 
detecting at a consumable-supplies condition detection unit of the customer equipment whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
displaying a purchase-order message related to the consumable-supplies, on the display when the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity; and 
transmitting a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when a purchase-order operation is performed on the operation panel in response to the displayed message.

10. A consumable-supplies purchase order system including a customer equipment and a purchase-order processing apparatus that are connected via a communication network, the customer equipment comprising: 
a consumable-supplies condition detection unit detecting whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
a transmission unit transmitting a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when the detection unit detects that the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity; 
a receiving unit receiving an order-reception message sent by the purchase-order processing apparatus when the purchase order is received at the purchase-order processing apparatus; and 
a displaying unit displaying an indication of completion of the purchase order on an operation panel of the customer equipment after the order-reception message is received.

11. A consumable-supplies purchase order system including a customer equipment and a purchase-order processing apparatus that are connected via a communication network, the customer equipment comprising: 
an operation panel having a display and a purchase-order button in the customer equipment; 
a consumable-supplies condition detection unit detecting whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
a displaying unit displaying a purchase-order message related to the consumable-supplies, on the display when the detection unit detects that the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity; 
a setting unit setting the purchase-order button in an active state; and 
a transmission unit transmitting a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when the purchase-order button is pressed.

12. A consumable-supplies purchase order system including a customer equipment and a purchase-order processing apparatus that are connected via a communication network, the customer equipment comprising: 
an operation panel having a display in the customer equipment; 
a consumable-supplies condition detection unit detecting whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
a displaying unit displaying a purchase-order message related to the consumable-supplies, on the display when the detection unit detects that the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity; and 
a transmission unit transmitting a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when a purchase-order operation is performed on the operation panel in response to the displayed message.

15. A customer equipment which is connected to a purchase-order processing apparatus via a communication network in a consumable-supplies purchase order system, the customer equipment comprising: 
a main controller; 
a communication controller; and 
a consumable-supplies condition detection unit detecting whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
wherein the main controller causes the communication controller to transmit a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when the detection unit detects that the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity.

17. A customer equipment which is connected to a purchase-order processing apparatus via a communication network in a consumable-supplies purchase order system, the customer equipment comprising: 
a main controller; 
a communication controller; 
a consumable-supplies condition detection unit detecting whether a quantity of consumable supplies in the customer equipment is less than a given reference quantity; 
an operation panel having a display and a purchase-order button in the customer equipment; and 
an operation panel controller controlling the operation panel; 
wherein the main controller causes the operation panel controller to display a purchase-order message related to the consumable-supplies, on the display when the detection unit detects that the quantity of the consumable supplies is less than the reference quantity, the main controller setting the purchase-order button in an active state, 
wherein the main controller causes the communication controller to transmit a consumable-supplies purchase order from the customer equipment to the purchase-order processing apparatus when the purchase-order button is pressed.

